description: Reviewer rules — code review checklist, rejection criteria
globs: src/**/*.{ts,tsx}

## Reviewer Checklist
1. Architecture follows Vertical Slice rules
2. No security vulnerabilities (XSS, injection, exposed keys)
3. Performance: no unnecessary re-renders, lazy loading in place
4. Clean code: no dead code, no console.log, no commented code
5. Responsive: works at all breakpoints
6. Dark mode: all new UI has dark: variants
7. DRY: no code duplication
8. Types: no `any`, proper interfaces
9. Tests: new code has tests covering edge cases
10. Build: `pnpm build` passes with zero errors
